OL,5, A lawyer for Windrush victims says the 
OL,6, government must publish a report which 
OL,7, suggests institutional racism at the   
OL,8, Home Office caused the scandal.        
OL,10,FThe report, seen by the BBC, says UK   
OL,11,Fimmigration laws from 1950 to 1981 were
OL,12,Fdesigned in part to "reduce the number 
OL,13,Fof black or brown people".             
OL,15,FIt also found these laws negatively    
OL,16,Faffected black people more than other  
OL,17,Fminority groups.                       
OL,19,FThe Home Office said the report was by 
OL,20,Fan independent author, and not policy. 
